@startuml TimerFlow
title METRIC - Motor do Timer (Local-First)
participant UI
participant TimerEngine
participant RxDB
participant SyncEngine

UI -> TimerEngine: StartTimer(taskId)
TimerEngine -> RxDB: Create TimeEntry {status: 'running'}
loop Cada 1 segundo
    TimerEngine -> UI: Update Display Tick
end
User -> UI: Pause/Stop
UI -> TimerEngine: Stop()
TimerEngine -> RxDB: Update TimeEntry {endTime, duration}
TimerEngine -> SyncEngine: Trigger Background Sync
@enduml
